overview:
LakeFrog.com is a dedicated real estate engine which allows real estate professionals and homeowners to connect with potential lake property home buyers across the United States.

For home buyers and renters, LakeFrog aims to provide the best-in-class search and browsing experience to find their dream lake area property. For real estate professionals and homeowners, LakeFrog provides an easy to use listing service along with insights on which type of lake area properties are at the top of the current market.

Our features include:

* Free posting of listings for all lakefront and lake area properties
* Nationwide coverage
* Integrated map technology
* Innovative listing features
* Direct contact system to connect potential homebuyers with real estate professionals and FSBOs
* Data and insights for lake area properties
